@startuml
title How the fair ticket price is found
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam ActivityBackgroundColor #EAF6F0
skinparam ActivityBorderColor #2E8B67
skinparam ActivityDiamondBackgroundColor #F5FBF8
skinparam ActivityDiamondBorderColor #2E8B67
skinparam ArrowColor #2E8B67

start
:Someone wants a "buy later" ticket;
:Stop guessing where the price is heading;
:Own a bike and sell tickets\nin a careful balanced mix;
:The mix is now safe\n(gains and losses cancel);
:A safe mix must grow\nat the plain bank rate;
:That rule leaves only ONE\nfair price for the ticket;
:Measure how jumpy the price is\n(jumpier means pricier);
:Keep nudging the balance\nas the price moves;
stop
@enduml
